snippet.title: JumpStart Kindergarten (1994)
snippet.description:
Longplay of the JumpStart that started it all.

JumpStart Kindergarten is a grade-based JumpStart game developed by Fanfare Software and released by Knowledge Adventure in 1994. JumpStart Kindergarten was the first installment in the JumpStart series, as well as Knowledge Adventure's first curriculum-based product.
